\v 12 It for that cause¦139715 that I am suffering¦139718 \add here in prison\add*, but I'm not ashamed¦139721 because I know who it is that I trust and I'm convinced that he is powerful¦139729 enough to guard¦139734 my deposit¦139732 \add of hope in him\add* until the end \add of this age\add*.
